7e5cdf1c-878d-4184-a0e0-893b0002ccda.name: KIVIK
7e5cdf1c-878d-4184-a0e0-893b0002ccda.description: Cuddle up in the comfortable KIVIK sofa. The generous size, low armrests and pocket springs with foam that adapts to the body invites you and your guests to many hours of socializing and relaxation.

701df2fd-8348-4e6d-ba28-e470042c15d7.name: FINNALA
701df2fd-8348-4e6d-ba28-e470042c15d7.description: FINNALA sectional sofa can grow and change with a home and the family. Choose how many seats, the look and function to create a sofa that suits you. A clean design and long-lasting comfort are included.

bc467258-c3c1-47ab-9a13-004fb095b408.name: LINANÄS
bc467258-c3c1-47ab-9a13-004fb095b408.description: This cover is made from Vissle fabric in polyester, which is dope-dyed. It’s a durable material with a smooth weave and a nice two-tone effect.

1c301890-569c-4a97-b56b-745024debaac.name: GAMMALBYN
1c301890-569c-4a97-b56b-745024debaac.description: Watch movies or talk to a friend. Read a book or take a break with the family. Email or sleep. Here’s space for everything in your life. Moveable cushions make the sofa comfy for sitting on and lying down.

0260e328-61b2-4f7e-8a59-0efffd7ebbe3.name: ÄPPLARYD
0260e328-61b2-4f7e-8a59-0efffd7ebbe3.description: ÄPPLARYD sofa will be your home’s comfy oasis. An eye-catcher that reflects your personality and style. Great to sit, lie down and hang out on. And with lots of space for the whole family, year after year.

4cb1b921-5777-4034-94b8-0facda41fe59.name: MORABO
4cb1b921-5777-4034-94b8-0facda41fe59.description: Warm and welcoming, neat and stylish. The supporting seat cushions, the cover’s soft finish and the tight fit gives this sofa a perfect balance between its comfort, functions and look.

a4de47ac-1473-4122-8bb9-d84787099a79.name: EKEDALEN
a4de47ac-1473-4122-8bb9-d84787099a79.description: A durable dining table that makes it easy to have big dinners. A single person can extend the table and there’s plenty of room for chairs since the legs are always located at the corners of the table.

0c9c98d9-a2a4-401b-823b-863b9fb050e7.name: INGATORP
0c9c98d9-a2a4-401b-823b-863b9fb050e7.description: Everyone faces each other around a round table and you can make room for socializing by simply adding a leaf. A traditional look with details like the turned leg gives it that little extra.

8793cbc1-8e5f-4e06-8383-0afe19772dcb.name: LISABO
8793cbc1-8e5f-4e06-8383-0afe19772dcb.description: Beautiful in its simplicity with a warm, natural wooden look. The innovative construction is very sturdy and with just a few clicks, the table is assembled and ready for use.

a4ea39cb-c484-40d4-ad53-b932f3b5d1de.name: NORDEN
a4ea39cb-c484-40d4-ad53-b932f3b5d1de.description: Gateleg tables have been around for centuries – with the space-saving design it’s no wonder why. We gave this table a straightforward, Scandinavian look and added a few drawers for flatware and napkins.

39d2d347-2657-4ee9-93e7-f7bbfd276b95.name: TARSELE
39d2d347-2657-4ee9-93e7-f7bbfd276b95.description: This extendable dining table is a nice mix of warm oak veneer and sturdy solid metal, and is inspired by 1950s industrial design. The table top also hides an extension leaf – perfect when you have guests.
